secubox-soc-agent (1.0.0-1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Implements SOC Agent for edge node monitoring
  * Features:
    - System metrics collection (CPU, memory, disk, network)
    - Security alert aggregation (CrowdSec, Suricata, WAF)
    - HMAC-SHA256 signed metric push to upstream SOC
    - Remote command execution with signature validation
    - SOC gateway enrollment workflow
    - Command audit logging

 -- Gerald KERMA <devel@cybermind.fr>  Tue, 01 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0200
